rows.label: qst200211_msg0001
rows.name: Thank you, mo! You saved me, mo!

rows.label: qst200211_msg0002
rows.name:
Don't worry about it! I
only did what was natural.

rows.label: qst200211_msg0003
rows.name:
By the way, what were you doing
in such a dangerous place?

rows.label: qst200211_msg0006
rows.name: What kind of products do you handle?

rows.label: qst200211_msg0007
rows.name:
Show me for a bit. I might be able
to buy something for you, yeah?

rows.label: qst200211_msg0008
rows.name: Ugh[ML:Dash ] P-products are not here now, mo.

rows.label: qst200211_msg0009
rows.name:
What? You don't have products
despite being a peddler?

rows.label: qst200211_msg0010
rows.name:
Mo-mo-mo[ML:Dash ] Th-the monsters from
earlier stole them, mo!

rows.label: qst200211_msg0011
rows.name: What did you say!? That's terrible!

rows.label: qst200211_msg0012
rows.name:
But, those guys weren't
holding anything?

rows.label: qst200211_msg0014
rows.name:
This Nopon[ML:Dash ] His behavior has been
suspicious for a while now.

rows.label: qst200211_msg0015
rows.name:
Yeah, looks like he's hiding
something. Shall we try to uncover it[ML:Dash ]
